lyrics_text:
[intro]
[verse]

Running in the night
My heart beats like a drum
I'm searching for the light
In this city so cold

I can feel the beat! (beat.... beat... beat...)
It's calling out my name
It's the city's melody
and it's ours to claim!

[chorus]

In the neon glow, we're betting it all
We'll keep on running
When all goes dark, our heart's final call
We'll keep on running
In the night's embrace, we'll find our way
We'll keep on running till the end of days!
Keep on running...
Keep on running...

[verse]

Staring at the sky
Searching for a sign
Our fates are intertwined
In these neon colored nights

I can be your star
and guide you through the night
Through the city's crowded streets,
We'll shine so bright!

[chorus]

In the neon glow, we're betting it all
We'll keep on running
When all goes dark, our heart's final call
We'll keep on running
In the night's embrace, we'll find our way
We'll keep on running till the end of days!
Keep on running...
Keep on running...

[bridge]

Now we're moving at the speed of light
There's nothing that can slow us down

We'll paint the city  in our shades
We'll keep on running till the end of days

[chorus]

In the neon glow, we're betting it all
We'll keep on running
When all goes dark, our heart's final call
We'll keep on running
In the night's embrace, we'll find our way
We'll keep on running till the end of days!
Keep on running...
Keep on running...

[outro]
